Body SVG path data AND the Body component implementation (Body.tsx,
components/SvgFemaleWrapper.tsx, components/SvgMaleWrapper.tsx) are adapted
from react-muscle-highlighter
(https://github.com/soroojshehryar/react-muscle-highlighter), MIT licensed,
Copyright (c) Sorooj Shehryar.

Modifications: the `Body` component was rewritten to support per-side
coloring — the original keyed user data by `slug` only and force-painted the
unmarked side with `defaultFill`, which made simultaneous left/right coloring
of the same body part impossible. The vendored version keys user data by
`${slug}|${side}` and looks up styles independently per path-side.

